For a complex task that requires making a call and then using the result to make another call, the API managed to make the first call and select the right tools for the next ones, but very often, it sent it as text (json) instead of as 'tool_calls'. 

This is with 'mistral_large_latest' 
The tools are correctly defined and works well most of the time (with simple prompts).

Sorrry if it is not the good place for this bug, I do not know how to post it. Discord says "I'm unable to assist with that request as it goes against our policies. " ?!!
